 ⚡ Eric Muli Makau — System Architecture & Portfolio Ecosystem


Welcome to the central tracking repository for my personal digital ecosystem. This single-page application highlights structural data flows, academic projects, blockchain systems engineering, and architectural principles.



 🚀 Key Functional Features

- **Algorithmic User Interface**: Modern, performance-tuned dark mode aesthetic built utilizing system-optimized CSS typography variables.
- **Dynamic Structural Interaction Pipeline**: Smooth scroll tracking and fluid reveal-on-scroll animations built with highly optimized Javascript Intersection Observers.
- **Asynchronous Event-Driven Messaging**: Replaced structural block-alerts with non-blocking custom runtime alert injection arrays.
- **Fluid Grid Architecture**: Fully adapted across dynamic device display grids (Mobile, Tablet, Desktop monitors).



 🛠 Tech Stack Configuration

- **Structural Layout:** HTML5 (Semantic Schema)
- **Styling Architecture:** CSS3 (Custom Properties & Grid Engines)
- **Execution Engine:** Vanilla JavaScript (ES6+ Asynchronous DOM Operations)



